  "description": "Supersaw + FM compound oscillator: OscA is the supersaw anchor, OscB is the FM satellite orbiting it. Drift depth at 0.48 means OscB wanders around OscA continuously, never settling on the same harmonic ratio twice. A foundational wandering pad.",
