    "revelation": "The supersaw provides the constant; the FM+drift provides the variable. Together they produce a sound that is oriented but not fixed.",
    "diagnosis": "Wander Path is the most approachable Transcendental Odyssey preset — a Supersaw+FM compound that any producer will find immediately useful. OscA=Supersaw for the density, OscB=FM at 0.28 depth for the character. Drift at 0.48 creates harmonic wandering in the FM satellite."
